OL,6,FMs James, a Democrat, sued Trump over
OL,7,Fwhat she said was not just harmless
OL,8,Fbragging but years of deceptive
OL,9,Fpractices.
OL,11,F"In a massive victory, we won our case
OL,12,Fagainst Donald Trump for engaging in
OL,13,Fyears of incredible financial fraud to
OL,14,Fenrich himself," James said on X,
OL,15,Fformerly Twitter.
OL,17,FBy making himself seem richer, Trump
OL,18,Fqualified for better loan terms, saved
OL,19,Fon interest and was able to complete
OL,20,Fprojects he might otherwise not have
OL,21,Ffinished, state lawyers said.
