OL,6,FJudge Arthur Engoron issued his
OL,7,Fdecision on Friday after a trial which
OL,8,Flasted over two months, that saw the
OL,9,FRepublican presidential front-runner
OL,10,Fbristling under oath that he was the
OL,11,Fvictim of a rigged legal system.
OL,13,FIn response to the verdict, Trump
OL,14,Fslammed the decision as a "complete
OL,15,Fand total sham" and called the trial a
OL,16,F"witch hunt."
